<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-MCw98/SFnGE8fJT3GXwEOngsV7Zt27NXFoaoApmYm81iuXoPkFOJwJ8ERdknLPMO" crossorigin="anonymous">
<title></title>
<style>
.card { border: 0;}
.card-header { border: 0; background-color: white; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.5em; }
.card-body { font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 2em; }
.footer {
   position: fixed;
   left: 0;
   bottom: 0;
   width: 100%;
}
hr { border-style: double; color: black; }
table,td { border: none; }
li { list-style-type: square; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
  J. JAVIER NÚÑEZ MARTÍN <span class="float-right">jj.nunezmartin@gmail.com </span> <br> Abogado - Lawyer <span class="float-right">Teléfono: 690.31.66.36 </span> <br> C/ Quiroga, Nº 1 – 2º E. <span class="float-right">Fax: 928.81.00.46</span> <br> Arrecife

  <hr style="border-top: 1px solid #000;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
      color: #fff;
      background-color: #fff;
      height: 6px;">


  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
  <div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6">

  <p><span class="font-weight-bold">FACTURA Nº:</span>  {{invoice.code}} </p>

  <p><span class="font-weight-bold">CLIENTE:</span>  {{invoice.expedient.client.name}} </p>

  <p><span class="font-weight-bold">CONCEPTO:</span>  {{invoice.kind}} </p>

  </div>





  </div>

  <div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6">
  <br>
  <p>En Arrecife a {{invoice.created|date('d/m/Y ')}}</p>
  <br>
  <p>Minuta de honorarios que presenta el abogado Don Jesús Javier Núñez Martín, con D.N.I. número 78553103-F a D./Dª. {{invoice.expedient.client.name}} en concepto de {{invoice.concept}}</p>

  </div>





  </div>


  <div class="row">

  <div class="col-sm6">

  <br><br>

  {% for concept in invoice.invoiceconcepts %}

  <p ><li style="padding-left: 3em; padding-right: 3em;"> {{concept.concept}}   <span class="float-right">{{concept.amount}}€</span></li></p>


  {% endfor %}



  </div>

  </div>

  <div class="row">

  <div class="col-sm6">

  <br><br>



  <p ><li style="padding-left: 3em; padding-right: 3em;"> <span class="font-weight-bold">Total</span>   <span class="float-right">{{invoice.amount}}€</span></li></p>



  </div>

  </div>


  <div class="footer">
    <p style="padding-left: 10%; padding-right: 10%; text-align: center; font-size: 0.9em;">Esta cantidad puede hacerla efectiva mediante ingreso en la cuenta corriente de Bankia número <span class="font-weight-bold">ES80 2038 1735 9060 0068 7520</span> titularidad del Letrado que suscribe esta factura.</p>

  </div>

  </div>
  </div>

  </body>
</html>
